<Project Sdk="Microsoft.NET.Sdk">

  <PropertyGroup>
    <TargetFramework>netstandard2.0</TargetFramework>
    <Version>0.9.2</Version>
    <PackageProjectUrl>https://github.com/AlexanderOnTesting/NetCoreWebDriverFactory</PackageProjectUrl>
    <PackageLicenseExpression>Apache-2.0</PackageLicenseExpression>
    <Company>AlexanderOnTest.tech</Company>
    <Authors>Alexander Dunn</Authors>
    <Product>WebDriverFactoryNunitConfig</Product>
    <PackageTags>Selenium, WebDriverFactory, WebDriver, Selenium WebDriver, DotNet Core, .net Core., NetCoreWebDriverFactory</PackageTags>
    <Copyright>Copyright 2019 Alexander Dunn</Copyright>
    <Description>Pick up NetCoreWebDriverFactory configuration for Nunit 3 test projects from runsettings files and with local file overrides.

Sample Runsettings file.

&lt;?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?&gt;
&lt;RunSettings&gt;
  &lt;TestRunParameters&gt;
    &lt;Parameter name="browserType" value="Chrome" /&gt;
    &lt;Parameter name="isLocal" value="true" /&gt;
    &lt;Parameter name="platform" value="Windows" /&gt;
    &lt;Parameter name="headless" value="false" /&gt;
    &lt;Parameter name="windowSize" value="FHd" /&gt;
  &lt;/TestRunParameters&gt;
&lt;/RunSettings&gt;

Overide files should be placed in 'My Documents' on Windows or '/' on Linux / MacOS

To overide the Grid URI a file called 'Config_GridUri.json' containing just the URI is required
e.g.
"http://192.168.0.200:4444/wd/hub"

To overide the complete WebDriverConfiguration a file called 'Config_WebDriver.json' is required
e.g.
{
  "Browser": "CHROME",
  "IsLocal": false,
  "PlatformType": "LINUX",
  "WindowSize": "HD",
  "GridUri": "http://192.168.0.200:4444/wd/hub"
}</Description>
    <PackageReleaseNotes>Initial release</PackageReleaseNotes>
    <GeneratePackageOnBuild>true</GeneratePackageOnBuild>
    <PackageId>Selenium.WebDriver.WebDriverFactoryNunitConfig</PackageId>
  </PropertyGroup>

  <ItemGroup>
    <PackageReference Include="NUnit" Version="3.11.0" />
    <PackageReference Include="Selenium.WebDriver.NetCoreWebDriverFactory" Version="2.2.0-alpha2" />
  </ItemGroup>

</Project>
